Then we have a problem, says the winter officer, "because then no one is ready to make room for the scattering vehicle."
Only after that, if it does not continue to snow, will it be the turn of feeder and development roads, including the Rat-Beil-Straße.
The last priority is side and side roads.
There will be complaints there, Brauburger knows.
